flowRoot.flowPara: This is my third online portfolio. It took me 3 years to get to this stage. During this time I almost finished I studies in college, went to England to study for real, cooked a lot of meals, met a ot of people, became freelance and worked for two agencies, wrote over 100 000 words, worked on 25+ projects... Heck, I even went on a Eurotrip and visited 27 cities in 22 days. By train. And much more.. What I can show you, are some pieces of the journey of how I got here.
